OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMotherland star Anna Maxwell Martin
OL,8,Fand a group of parents are warning
OL,9,Fthat primary school tests have
OL,10,F"devastating effects" for children
OL,11,Fwith special educational needs and
OL,12,Fdisabilities (Send).
OL,14,FAlong with 22 parent groups and
OL,15,Fcampaigners, Maxwell Martin, who has
OL,16,Fspoken previously about navigating the
OL,17,FSend system as a parent, is calling on
OL,18,Fthe Education Secretary to reconsider
OL,19,Freforming primary Sats.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@UO]
