OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThey are delivering an open letter to
OL,8,FBridget Phillipson on Tuesday which
OL,9,Fsays the current Sats system "actively
OL,10,Fharms" children with Send, leaving
OL,11,Fthem often disengaged from school as
OL,12,Fthey move on to secondary.
OL,14,FMaxwell Martin said: "The Government
OL,15,Fneeds to look much harder at how to
OL,16,Fmake things better for children in
OL,17,Fschools, particularly children with
OL,18,FSend."
