OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe large proportion of children with
OL,8,FSend who failed Sats "spend their
OL,9,Fentire year 6 convinced they are not
OL,10,Fclever enough", the open letter stated.
OL,12,F"They feel they don't belong. They try
OL,13,Fharder every day, but the odds are so
OL,14,Fstacked against them that the weight
OL,15,Fof it all eventually breaks them," it
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FThe Government said last week, in its
OL,19,Fresponse to the curriculum review,
OL,20,Fthat it had "no plans to radically
OL,21,Fchange the shape" of primary tests.
