OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FIt would make some changes to how
OL,8,Fwriting was assessed, and grammar and
OL,9,Fpunctuation. There would be more
OL,10,Fsupport for children with Send to
OL,11,Faccess phonics in year 1 to improve
OL,12,Ftheir reading, but only minor
OL,13,Famendments were suggested to year 6
OL,14,FSats.
OL,16,FThe letter signatories said the
OL,17,Fcurrent Sats system narrowed the
OL,18,Fcurriculum and encouraged teaching to
OL,19,Fthe test.
