OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Forcing children into a system that
OL,8,Factively harms them is not the answer.
OL,9,FChanging the system so that our
OL,10,Fchildren want to attend is," the
OL,11,Fletter said.
OL,13,F"The run-up to secondary school is
OL,14,Falready a vulnerable time. Just when
OL,15,Fwe want to work with schools to build
OL,16,Fconfidence, Sats dismantle it`leaving
OL,17,Fself-esteem and nervous systems in
OL,18,Ftatters.
