OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FBut Education Secretary Bridget
OL,8,FPhillipson announced recently that
OL,9,Fthis would be delayed until 2026 to
OL,10,Fallow more time to test reform
OL,11,Fproposals with families as well as
OL,12,Fteachers and experts.
OL,14,FSend parent Kirsti Hadley, from
OL,15,Fconsultancy and campaign group
OL,16,FGeneration Alphabet, said: "Ahead of
OL,17,Fthe Schools White Paper, Bridget
OL,18,FPhillipson has said she wants to
OL,19,Flisten to parents, especially parents
OL,20,Fof children with Send.
OL,26,@xD@\OU
