OL,3,CSats 'devastating' for Send pupils,
OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"So, we are saying loud and clear:
OL,8,Fthink again about Sats. Forcing
OL,9,Fchildren into a system that actively
OL,10,Fharms them is not the answer. Changing
OL,11,Fthe system so that our children want
OL,12,Fto attend school is."
OL,14,FSarah Hannafin, head of policy at
OL,15,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said there
OL,16,Fis an "urgent need" for the Government
OL,17,Fto rethink the value of Sats.
