OL,4,CMotherland star and parent campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"If statutory tests are here to stay,
OL,8,Fthey must be designed to be accessible
OL,9,Ffor the vast majority of pupils, they
OL,10,Fshould recognise the attainment and
OL,11,Fprogress of all children, and they
OL,12,Fshould not damage children's
OL,13,Fconfidence or cause distress," she
OL,14,Fadded.
